{"tid":1789520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣唔俾黑警爆入Iphone教學(附圖)","createTime":"2019-12-19T11:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T11:47:40.000Z","uid":310216,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8642a3b293bea1d37496cd9723c60157f72e38b4","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"小弟平時無聊會研究ios setting入面既野 以下係所得出既結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想好似黃之鋒Iphone被人爆 大家可以咁做<br />\n只限Iphone...(睇你係咩機種)<br />\nface id解鎖機種 (iphone10或以上機種)<br />\n指紋解鎖(iphone 8以下機種)<br />\n呢啲大家都知啦？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 1: sim card lock (大家一定要記得個密碼)</strong><br />\n呢個好基本啦  好耐之前大家應該有set到啦 未set就自己爬文搞啦 個密碼最好就自己寫係備忘錄啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 2: 閂左siri個function</strong><br />\n因爲好多時ios啲bug係由siri trigger出黎 啲bug可以爆入部機 可能睇到你啲資料 所以盡量唔好用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 3: update到最新ios (而家係13.3)</strong><br />\n舊機種就盡量唔好用啦 最好用ios 13 support緊既機(iphone 6s或以上個啲)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 4: 閂曬鎖定時允許使用既選項</strong><br />\n因爲黑警開唔到你部機 一定會想透過以下既功能用bug爆入你部機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5FrZHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5FrZHB.png&h=18625588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 5: 開10次錯誤密碼清除資料</strong><br />\n呢個大家應該知點解啦 黑警試完十次密碼之後就會鎖機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXzXmWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXzXmWr.png&h=77432e3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 6: set個好啲既密碼啊大佬</strong><br />\n唔好再用0000 個啲既密碼 大家最好唔好用4位或6位密碼 用其他自訂密碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YABrfgc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYABrfgc.png&h=01ec3d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 7: 唔用指紋或face id做解鎖</strong><br />\n剩係用密碼解鎖 (只限做到最安全)<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法係做到最絕 得返密碼俾佢試<br />\n<br />\n<strong>step 8: 用face id既人一定要開 (圖)</strong><br />\n如果你咁唔好彩被黑警拉左同恐嚇緊 逼你用face id開 你就死都唔好開眼 咁佢就開唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ajv0jJh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjv0jJh.png&h=ad53df1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲有其他方法 歡迎大家可以係下面討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23af2d4aaf28fa811e2130d18918a020253d0169","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"有無人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627a068baca1ec15c1e8030a92702aa48c1c38bf","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到啊啊啊啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da70347082c586af554d79311ba5bb1c798c42b5","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"447adc9dba99310514d06e0d3e56bf810895a3d4","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"二推"},{"pid":"ac110a6bc0cef52b2bfc92cf26f8960c363fa10e","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"三推"},{"pid":"5f019e747a53d8b8d5ab3c0a338295c3871730ce","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"四推"},{"pid":"70493b252ba349383e29897df701ffab5758629d","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"五推"},{"pid":"44571cc714d4526bf786be2b2266c8c23aef5fc7","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"六推"},{"pid":"ed2c32b72e671794773381cf1a6c44b8dc573e3b","tid":1789520,"uid":310216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"七推"},{"pid":"b9043e43d2fa28abe4d1e825636f5b87fa6811a4","tid":1789520,"uid":320976,"like":